Inside Macintosh: Cyberdog Programmer's Kit / Part 3 - Cyberdog Reference
Chapter 6 - Types, Constants, and Global Functions / Types and Constants
Log

Log Kinds

The following constants represent different ways that Cyberdog items can be displayed by the Cyberdog log. The Cyberdog log uses these constants in its stored representation.

kLogKindAlphabetical
Log entries are listed alphabetically.
kLogKindChronological
Log entries are listed chronologically.
kLogKindHierarchical
Log entries are listed hierarchically.
